<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2004-08-26</DATELINE><TITLE>Virology on the Internet: the time is right for a new journal</TITLE><BODY>Virology Journal is an exclusively on-line, Open Access journal devoted to the presentation of high-quality original research concerning human, animal, plant, insect bacterial, and fungal viruses. Virology Journal will establish a strategic alternative to the traditional virology communication process.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>